overview: RocketRelief.com is a new, cutting edge answer to the age old problem of handling tax disputes with the IRS. Rocket Relief is an Internet company that connects taxpayers across the country with tax experts who resolve tax problems. Rocket Relief is far easier than finding tax experts on your own. Rocket Relief saves you the hassle of picking the best among thousands of attorneys - we deliver the right tax experts, under contract, right to your inbox. We have indexed our tax experts to specific tax issues they can solve, so all you have to do is tell us about your situation and we can match it with a tax expert certified to assist in resolving it.
